import React from 'react'
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row'
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col'
import Jumbo from 'react-bootstrap/Jumbotron'
import Image from 'react-bootstrap/Image'
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button'
import Mes from './Mes'

export default function Calendario() {
const vecColores=['#5d29bf','#e77cdb','#0565ad','#173c51','#603912','#75dace','#ab079d','#62c33d','#9f0f56','#1a39e9','#531911','#87c4d7','#d0c20e','#772f92','#304fd7','#4db650','#186468','#1d27b4','#63aee0','#b7622f','#46e6df','#ef34f4','#435b15','#da8570','#d7db92','#1597d0','#085ef5','#e3aac7','#56d2cf','#8070a4']

    return (
        <>
            <Container>
                <Row>
                    <Col>
                        <Mes />
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        </>
    )
}
